ionally adding the optional io.vertx:vertx-auth-oauth2 dependency.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Local Gradle and native-image verification remain authoritative; the issue is specifically a JDK 25 current-defaults native-image run failure.\",\n    \"The io.vertx:vertx-web-client artifact declares io.vertx:vertx-auth-oauth2 as optional, so generated tests that exercise OAuth2WebClient without adding that dependency may fail to compile or run.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0adbfa442e8ea99f016a3e7b0e62e48197be229998ed43a49e\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 6481, "output": 808, "cacheRead": 29696, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 36985, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782479617717, "responseId": "resp_0adbfa442e8ea99f016a3e7b022ab481979bda4c4b83443b55"}}
